Title of the Project: EduRide: School Transport Platform

Description of the Project:
EduRide is a web-based Application that automates and manages the daily school bus transportation process.
It connects school, bus agencies, drivers, helpers, teachers and parents in one digital system.

Software Requirements for the Project:
Frontend: React.js (18.2)
Backend: Spring Boot (3.5.7)
Database: MySQL (8.0)
Testing tool: POSTMAN (API testing) / Swagger
Version Control: GitHub
IDE: Spring Tools Suite (STS 4.3.0)

Hardware Requirements for the Project
RAM: 8GB or above
Hard Disk: 100 GB free space
Internet Connection
Processor: intel i3 or above
